  <data key="d0">Colour</data>
  <data key="d1">section</data>
  <data key="d2">A section of the field guide describing the colour of P. echinaster, ranging from deep orange to red or pure white, with light red to yellowish white spines and pale oral surface.&lt;SEP&gt;A section heading in the document about the colour of the organism; no colour description is provided in the input text.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b7d87a9fdd6796fbc3a24c40022179ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6312bf3bcdf9b3397dffc439b6ad9d04</data>
