  <data key="d0">Size</data>
  <data key="d1">section</data>
  <data key="d2">A section of the field guide describing the size of P. echinaster, averaging 50 to 160 mm in diameter.&lt;SEP&gt;The Size section describes the dimensions of the featured marine invertebrate.</data>
