<node id="Inflation Behavior">
  <data key="d0">Inflation Behavior</data>
  <data key="d1">behavior</data>
  <data key="d2">The behavior of inflating when landed is characteristic of Spoladaster Brachyactis; Chondraster Elattosis does not inflate.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-21ece0344bd87c400d1d234a341d632a</data>
