  <data key="d2">The third image in the document shows the distinct patterning on the aboral surface of the Thick Fleshy Starfish when brooding.&lt;SEP&gt;An image referenced in the distinguishing features text on page 430 of the field guide, showing the aboral surface patterning of the Inflexible Rigid Star during brooding.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c93021c72fb2fa03f2a5d62bc0adb874&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43c53974450202fe6a82416f946fc26f</data>
