<node id="References Section">
  <data key="d0">References Section</data>
  <data key="d1">section</data>
  <data key="d2">The References Section is a part of a field guide on invertebrates, specifically associated with document identifier doc_sa_invertebrates_p0429_0432. This section appears across pages 429, 430, and 431, and is explicitly labeled "references" on page 429. It contains reference information for an image of starfish, including a citation to the work "Starfishes of the Atlantic." Additionally, the section includes species identification notes and image content analysis metadata. Its neighbor text leads to a description of distinguishing features of the Phylum Echinodermata. The section serves as a bibliographic listing and also provides contextual metadata for identifying and differentiating the depicted organisms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c93021c72fb2fa03f2a5d62bc0adb874&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5bd15d157743c89b7fd9be20dd1df380&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01224e247c54c26376338d1d355035dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-272e62d6d62e10360c47dab598eb09e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2cad148e1c5a94e8c3f62bdfee2b66fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43c53974450202fe6a82416f946fc26f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37cbd16434444d9480d8632be65be39c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-193d40aeb45ee8e91a4034e163403a2b</data>
  <data key="d4">Field-Guide-to-SA-Offshore-Marine-Invertebrates_web-full-version_compressed.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1781097485</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
