<node id="Taxonomic classification of Chondraster elattosis (Pentagon star) (table)">
  <data key="d0">Taxonomic classification of Chondraster elattosis (Pentagon star) (table)</data>
  <data key="d1">table</data>
  <data key="d2">A two-column taxonomic hierarchy table for Chondraster elattosis, listing ranks from Phylum (Echinodermata) to Common name (Pentagon star). It supports the adjacent species description, reinforcing the pentagonal shape and providing formal classification that contextualizes the distribution, size, colour, and distinguishing features detailed on page 430 of the field guide.</data>
