<node id="Poraniopsis echinaster (Spiky cushion star) Taxonomic Classification Table (table)">
  <data key="d0">Poraniopsis echinaster (Spiky cushion star) Taxonomic Classification Table (table)</data>
  <data key="d1">table</data>
  <data key="d2">This table presents the full taxonomic hierarchy of Poraniopsis echinaster (Spiky cushion star), from phylum Echinodermata to species level. It complements the species description on page 432 by providing formal classification, reinforcing identification, and connecting morphological traits (e.g., spiky spines, cushion shape) with its scientific name. The table is sourced from a field guide and references authoritative works, serving as a quick reference for the organism's biological lineage.</data>
