<node id="Luidia Sarsii Africana">
  <data key="d0">Luidia Sarsii Africana</data>
  <data key="d1">species</data>
  <data key="d2">A subspecies or variety of starfish in the family Luidiidae, known by the common name "Legs break easily starfish" and characterized by arms that break off easily from the central disc.</data>
