<node id="Brooding">
  <data key="d0">Brooding</data>
  <data key="d1">behavior</data>
  <data key="d2">Brooding behavior of the Inflexible Rigid Star, indicated by very distinct patterning on the aboral surface.&lt;SEP&gt;The starfish exhibits brooding behavior, during which the aboral surface patterning becomes very distinct.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-01224e247c54c26376338d1d355035dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43c53974450202fe6a82416f946fc26f</data>
