<node id="Inflexible Rigid Star">
  <data key="d0">Inflexible Rigid Star</data>
  <data key="d1">species</data>
  <data key="d2">An inflexible, rigid star with a thick, solid, spongy disc, pentagonal shape, indistinct marginal plates, distinct madreporite, fine raised bumps (sheaths of adambulacral spines) forming distinct rows along each arm, no spines, thick fleshy with smooth aboral and oral surface, double rows of tube feet, and distinct patterning on the aboral surface when brooding.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-43c53974450202fe6a82416f946fc26f</data>
  <data key="d4">Field-Guide-to-SA-Offshore-Marine-Invertebrates_web-full-version_compressed.pdf</data>
